This item can be returned for credit card refund.

Please note that as a service to holiday shoppers, we will be extending returns on eligible items purchased between November 18, 2016 and December 31, 2016. Buyers will have until January 15, 2017 to request a return authorization (RMA) for items purchased between these dates, and will have until January 31, 2017 for the return to be received in our warehouse.
